''AKA Simple Linear Regression''

[[Univariate Regression|Univariate Linear Regression]] is a special case of [[Linear Regression]], when $$X$$ is [[Scalar]].

This special case is important because:

* It is pretty much the only case that can be conveniently visualised
* The derivations do not involve complex [[Linear Algebra]]

